 color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. Lawful purpose&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. Subscription to memorandum&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. public company - 7 or more person&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. private company - 2 or more persons&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. OPC - 1 person only&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. Filing of documents&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;D. Compliance of requirements of the Act&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot; id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-3a428123-7fff-9266-76dd-e21e731f5fbe&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. OPC&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;One Person Company’ means a company which has only one person as a member.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. Specific provisions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. ‘One Person Company’ shall be mentioned in brackets below the name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. OPC shall have 1 member only&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. minimum of 1 director&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;II. FORMATION OF OPC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. nominee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. OPC shall state: the name of any other person who shall become the member of the OPC in case of death or incapacity of member.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Nominee shall give written consent&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. withdrawal of consent by the nominee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. nominee shall give a notice in writing to the member and the OPC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. member shall nominate a new nominee within 15 days of receipt of the notice of withdrawal of consent by the nominee and within 30 days file with the Registrar the notice of withdrawal and written consent of the new nominee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; f