ot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. shall provide security for the due repayment of the amount of deposits and interest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Security shall&amp;nbsp; be provided by way of a charge on any asset excluding intangible assets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. shall not be created by way of pledge of any assets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. shall be created on -specific movable property or specific immovable property&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;5. amount of such deposits and interest thereon shall not exceed the market value of such&amp;nbsp; assets as assessed by a registered valuer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;6. security shall be created in favour of a trustee for the depositors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;H. Appointment of trustee for depositors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. company shall not issue any circular or advertisement inviting secured deposits unless&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;the company has appointed one or more trustees for depositors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. written consent shall be obtained from the trustee(s) for depositors before his / their appointment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. statement shall appear in the circular&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. shall execute a deposit trust deed in Form DPT-2 at least 7 days before issuing the circular&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;5. Person shall not be appointed as a trustee if --&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(i)&amp;nbsp; is a depositor in the company;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(ii)&amp;nbsp; is a director, key managerial personnel or any other officer or an employee of the company or of its holding, subsidiary or associate company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(iii)&amp;nbsp; is indebted to the company, or its subsidiary or its holding or associate company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(v)&amp;nbsp; has given any guarantee in respect of deposits accepted by the company or interest thereon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;vi) is related to any person specified in Points (i) or (ii) above.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;I. Duties of trustee(s) for depositors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. ensure that the assets of the company on which charge is created are sufficient to cover the repayment of the principal amount of secured deposits outstanding and interest thereon.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. circular or advertisement does not contain any information which is inconsistent with the terms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;3. ensure that the company does not commit any breach of provisions of the trust deed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;4. take steps to procure a remedy for any breach of provisions of the trust deed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;5. take steps to call a meeting of the holders of depositors as and when such meeting is required to be held.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;6. supervise the implementation of the conditions regarding creation of security&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;7. carry out such acts necessary for the protection of the interest of depositors and to resolve their grievances.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;J. Meeting of depositors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;a meeting of all the depositors shall be called by the trustee for depositors on requisition{official order laying claim} in writing signed by at least 1/10th of the depositors in value for the time being outstanding or in the happening of any event, which constitutes a default.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;K. Furnishing of deposit receipts to depositors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. company shall furnish to the depository receipt for the amount received by the company within 21 days from the date of receipt and shall be signed by an officer duly authorised&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. deposit receipt shall contain:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(i) date of deposit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(ii) name and address of the depositor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(iii)&amp;nbsp; amount received as deposit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(iv)&amp;nbsp; rate of interest payable on deposit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(v)&amp;nbsp; date on which the deposit is repayable.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(204 , 204 , 204) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;L. Registers of deposits[skipped]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;M. Return of deposits to be filed with the Registrar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#CCCCCC&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. company, shall, on or before the 30th day of June every year, file with the Registrar, a return in Form DPT-3 along with the prescribed fees and Such return shall be duly audited&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;N. Disclosures in the financial statement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(a)&amp;nbsp; Every company, other than a private company, shall disclose in its FS, by way of notes, about the money received from the directors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(b)&amp;nbsp; Every private company shall disclose in its FS, by way of notes, about the money received from the directors and relatives of directors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;(c)&amp;nbsp; Every company, other than Government company, shall file a one-time return of outstanding receipt of money or loan by it, but not considered as deposits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;O. Penal rate of interest&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. If a company fails to repay such a deposit, the company shall pay a penal rate of interest of &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;18% p.a for the overdue period.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;P. Punishment for contravention&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 72pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1.company and every officer in default-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. fine upto Rs. 5,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 108pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. Rs.500 for every day&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 18pt ; margin-bottom: 6pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;6. REPAYMENT OF DEPOSITS, ETC., ACCEPTED BEFORE COMMENCEMENT OF THE COMPANIES ACT, 2013&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;A. Filing of Statement and repayment of deposit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;accepted any deposit before the commencement of the Companies Act, 2013 and deposit or interest thereon remains unpaid company shall -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. file a Statement with the Registrar Within 3 months containing particulars of deposits and interest remaining unpaid and arrangements made for repayment of deposits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. repay such deposits within 3 years from the commencement or before expiry whichever is earlier&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;B. Extension of time for repayment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;1. company may make an application to the Tribunal seeking extension of time for repayment of any deposit accepted before the commencement of the Companies Act, 2013.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;2. Tribunal may allow such further time for repayment of deposits, as it may deem fit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;C. Punishment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; margin-left: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;If a company fails to repay the deposits or interest thereon in accordance within the time&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38 ; text-indent: 36pt ; margin-top: 0pt ; margin-bottom: 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; background-color: transparent ; font-weight: 400 ; font-style: normal ; font-variant: normal ; text-decoration: none ; vertical-align: baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: none ; display: inline-block ; overflow: hidden ; width: 602px ; height: 117px&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/krleK1CC4jS0durW3jg_TrOzWZo7b1XUHiUIGfaEH9S2XrXG1PClsZ1X5D2J91SQ7P2jMiiZUbzxO7dW0mae_z8wQwUlCkyS5ZPBysKcxuejXfGYE20qPIzZukfG3B9HbFlR2qBu=s0&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0px ; margin-top: 0px&quot; width=&quo